<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="stop-v">stop <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /stɒp/    美 /stɑːp/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>(使) 停止；防止；中断：</strong></h4>
<ul>
<li>stop doing sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>No matter how bad the weather is, she never stops running.
不管天气多么糟糕，她都不会停止跑步。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>stop sb / sth (from) doing sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Not being a winner didn’t stop my daughter from trying.
没有成为获奖者并没有阻止我的女儿继续努力。</p><footer>2016 天津改</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The UN will have to work hard to stop history from repeating itself.
联合国必须要努力使历史不再重演。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>stop to do sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Uncertain about how to fix them, she stopped to think carefully.
她不知道如何修理它们，于是停下来仔细思考。</p><footer>北师大⑥ – 16</footer></div>

<p>注: stop to do 表示停下来去做其他事情；stop doing 表示停止正在做的事情。  </p>
<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="stop-off-in-at">stop off (in / at)</h3>
<p>1.<strong>在…中途停留：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We stopped off in Barn for an hour on the way.
中途我们在巴恩停留了一个小时。</p><footer>2009 全国</footer></div></div>